.TH ABRAFLEXI-PULL-BANK 1 "July 17, 2026" "abraflexi-matcher" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
abraflexi-pull-bank \- Download online bank statements into AbraFlexi
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B abraflexi-pull-bank
.RI [ env_file ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B abraflexi-pull-bank
triggers AbraFlexi's own online bank statement download for the
configured company, without doing any invoice matching itself. Run it on
its own schedule ahead of the matcher scripts (which assume the bank
statements are already present and no longer pull them inline).
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.RI [ env_file ]
Path to the environment file to load configuration from (default:
.BR ../.env ).
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
.B ABRAFLEXI_URL
AbraFlexi server URL
.TP
.B ABRAFLEXI_LOGIN
AbraFlexi login username
.TP
.B ABRAFLEXI_PASSWORD
AbraFlexi password
.TP
.B ABRAFLEXI_COMPANY
AbraFlexi company code
.TP
.B MATCHER_LOCALIZE
Locale for log/report messages: en_US (default), cs_CZ, or sk_SK.
.TP
.B RESULT_FILE
Path to the output JSON report file.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Success.
.TP
.B 400
Bad request \- invalid data or parameters.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR abraflexi-matcher (1),
.BR abraflexi-match-varsym (1),
.BR abraflexi-match-specsym (1),
.BR abraflexi-match-accountno (1)
.SH AUTHOR
Written by Vitex Software.
